// ========================== CCFrax1to1AMM ===========================
// ====================================================================
// Crosschain Frax 1-to-1 AMM
// Uses Chainlink oracles and liquidity limits for security
// Swaps whitelisted stablecoins 1-to-1 with FRAX, and vice versa

